# Globally Distributed WebRTC Communication Platform — Part 1
## Architecture Overview, Edge & Signaling Layers

> **Target Scale**: 100M+ registered users · 10M+ concurrent WebSocket connections · 3M+ concurrent active calls
> **SLA**: 99.995% availability · <120ms global call setup latency
> **Stack**: Node.js · TypeScript · Fastify · tRPC · Redis Cluster · PostgreSQL · Kafka · Kubernetes

---

